 of the connected account'=>'Nome de usuario da conta conectada','Automatic protection and rule updates'=>'Protección automática e actualizacións de regras','Open overlay when filters are used outside the Jetpack Sidebar'=>'Abrir superposición cando os filtros se usen fóra da barra lateral de Jetpack','Jetpack AI Assistant brings the power of AI right into your WordPress editor, letting your content creation soar to new heights.'=>'Jetpack AI Assistant incorpora o poder da IA no teu editor de WordPress para que poidas mellorar as túas competencias en materia de creación de contido.','<p>Paid customers get dedicated email support from our world-class Happiness Engineers to help with any issue.</p>
